comment.text: This translation key is used to display a success message when a storage quota is successfully set. It is commonly displayed in dialogs and notifications after updating storage quotas, ensuring users are informed of the successful completion of the operation.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'kvotası' is a transliteration of 'quota' and while understandable, 'payı' would be a more natural Azerbaijani equivalent for 'quota' in this context.

The translation "Limit pamięci został pomyślnie ustawiony" doesn't fully capture the meaning of 'Storage quota.' 'Limit pamięci' translates to 'memory limit,' whereas 'Storage quota' refers to a limit on storage space (e.g., disk space).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Przydział miejsca na dysku został pomyślnie ustawiony.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Limită de stocare este stabilită cu succes' is a literal translation but doesn't convey the same natural flow as the English original. It sounds somewhat stiff and formal in Romanian.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Cota de stocare a fost stabilită cu succes.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'ආචයන සලාකය සැකසිණි' does not accurately convey the meaning of 'Storage quota successfully set.' 'ආචයන' is not a relevant word. 'සලාකය' loosely translates to 'slice' or 'portion,' which is not related to storage quota. 'සැකසිණි' means 'was decorated' or 'was arranged,' which doesn't fit the context of setting a quota.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A more accurate translation might be something like 'ගබඩාවේ උපරිමතොග සාර්ථකව සකස් කරන ලදි' (Gabadava uparimathoga sartthaka sahkasan ladi) which translates to 'Storage quota successfully set' or 'භාරක තොග සාර්ථකව සකස් කරන ලදි' (Bhaaraka thoga sartthaka sahkasan ladi), which translates to 'Storage limit successfully set.'

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Складишна квота успешно постављена' literally translates to 'Warehouse quota successfully set'. It's not an accurate representation of 'Storage quota'.  'Storage' should be translated as 'Захват' or 'Простор за складиштење'.
